    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride of ownership, offering a balanced blend of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, with only minor, unavoidable stone chips on the front bumper that do not detract from its overall presence. All body panels are straight and original. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the upholstery shows minimal wear on the driver's bolster, while the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, infotainment system, and heated seats, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a comprehensive service history detailing regular fluid changes and recent brake pad replacements. The tires are premium brand with roughly 70% tread life remaining. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. It is a smoke-free, well-documented vehicle that is ready for immediate daily use.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
