    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that's ready to hit the road today! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles. It's been super reliable for me, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
