    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is in solid form, having received critical rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The suspension geometry remains precise, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for optimal lateral grip. Recent service includes a valve lash adjustment and new rod bearings for peace of mind. This is a visceral, driver-centric machine maintained to a high mechanical standard, ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
